name: alloc::collections::btree::node::Handle::<collections::btree::node::NodeRef<collections::btree::node::marker::Dying, K, V, NodeType>, collections::btree::node::marker::KV>::drop_key_val
doc:
Drops the key and value that the KV handle refers to.
 # Safety
 The node that the handle refers to must not yet have been deallocated.
